GitNexus (architectural inspiration)
https://github.com/abhigyanpatwari/GitNexus

AgentNexus's `code-graph/` CLI is a workflow-driven, minimal reimplementation
inspired by GitNexus's design pattern (Kuzu-backed embedded code knowledge
graph with git lifecycle integration). No code is copied from GitNexus.

